guess4 <- ctmm.guess(Gus.2019, interactive= FALSE)
fit1 <- ctmm.select(Gus.all, guess1)
fit2 <- ctmm.select(Gus.2021, guess2)
fit3 <- ctmm.select(Gus.2020, guess3)
fit4 <- ctmm.select(Gus.2019, guess4)
summary(fit1) # n= 434
